comments[2]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-06-16T17:23:23.003Z",claude-code-agent,"Design decisions for GH-243 (pm comments edit/delete): (1) 1-based index matching list order. (2) Flags: --delete <index> and --edit <index>; replacement text from positional [text]/--add/--stdin/--file. (3) New ops comment_edit, comment_delete; allowlisted in bypassesAssigneeConflict under --allow-audit-comment. (4) Edit preserves original created_at+author, sets edited_at=nowIso(). (5) Extend runAnnotationCommand mode union with edit/delete; surface only on comments command."
  "2026-06-16T19:30:07.545Z",maintainer-agent,"Integration (lead): wired shared surfaces the sub-agent flagged — register-mutation comments command (--edit/--delete via new parsePositiveIntOption argParser), MCP pm_comments (isListing guard + description + param tables), completion bash/zsh, COMMENTS_FLAG_CONTRACTS + contracts golden, docs/COMMANDS.md. Refactored resolveCommentInput to reuse resolveCommentTextSource (removed duplication). Added full edit/delete + resolveAnnotationIndex + op-fallback + CLI-registration tests for 100% coverage."
close_reason: "Added: pm comments --edit/--delete lifecycle commands for obsolete-note cleanup."
